<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.5">
<l>cīroṉṟu tūtāyt turiyō taṉaṉpakka</l>
<l>lūroṉṟu vēṇṭip peṟāta vurōṭattāl</l>
<l>pāroṉṟip pāratam kaiceytu pārttaṟkut</l>
<l>tēroṉṟai yūrntāṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">tēvapi rāṉukkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring a staff for the one who,</l>
<l rend="indent">incarnating on earth as a great messenger,</l>
<l rend="indent">due to [his] anger at having requested a single city</l>
<l rend="indent">from Duryodhana and being denied,</l>
<l rend="indent">pledging [his] hand to the Bhārata war,</l>
<l>drove a chariot for Pārtha.</l>
<l>Bring a staff for the god of gods.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
